                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elio</ex></expan> Bito <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>le<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I</supplied>III <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> s&amp;lt;t&amp;gt;<expan><abbr>ip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>XV</abbr><ex cert="low"/>III</expan> <expan><abbr>titulu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>fecit <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Valentinus <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ustos</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>rmorum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>eius</abbr><ex>dem</ex></expan> <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>aeres</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/>fecit Bito <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>upra</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>cripto</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>vixit an<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>os</abbr></expan> XXXVIII <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ene</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erenti</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>uit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>In 3 Teile gebrochen; der mittlere Teil gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein Grab. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Kranz mit Rosette, darüber ein Giebelfeld; ganz oben horizontaler Abschluß, bekrönt von einem Altärchen in der Mitte und zwei liegenden Löwen an den Seiten. Buchstaben sehr ungleichmäßig und nicht bündig auf Zeilenhöhe angeordnet.</p>
            </div>
